dmca.title: Re: counterfeit Joe's Jeans
dmca.body:
In a message dated 3/9/2007 9:30:00 PM Pacific Standard Time, investigations@joesjeans.com writes:

Jane-

Please take down the counterfeit R&R jeans from your website.  Did you not agree to NOT post counterfeit  R&R and True Religion jeans on your website?
